Writhenset: Foes of the Free People
Foes of the Free Peoples found at Writhenset should be defeated in order protect those within the Wildwood.
Foes can be found at Writhenset in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should defeat foes at Writhenset.
Foes of the Free Peoples have claimed the mines of Writhenset beneath the Wildwood. Defeating their numbers here will assist in returning safety to the Wildwood.
